le. Zugleich lassen die untersuchten Produktionen in der Rezeption selbst nicht in Ruhe - und so stellt sich auch die Frage nach den hier wirksamen »Übergriffen« und Lustgewinnen.  aThe currently »aroused« cultural upheaval about children as figures is one starting point of this cultural study. This »arousal« turns out to be part of a social conflict: Things once repelled abundantly return in western images and discourses of child and youth sexuality. This volume analyzes art and media material which addresses trans-boundary aspects of sexuality. In a broad continuum, motives of abuse, »sexual degeneration«, loss of innocence, or even seduction play a role - to name a few. At the same time, the analyzed productions do not let go in their reception - and so the question of what »transgressions« and pleasure gains are at play here poses itself once more.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aCultural Studies. 4aKind. 4aKultur. 4aKultureller Wandel. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aKunst. 4aKörper. 4aMedien. 4aMedienästhetik. 4aPopuläre Kunst. 4aÜbergriff. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aArt.  aBody.  aChild.  aCultural Studies.  aCultural Transformation.  aCulture.  aMedia Aesthetics.  aMedia.  aPopular Art.1 aHärtel, Insa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWitte, Sonja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWitte, Sonja.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine 2014z9783110370379oZDB-23-DPM08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9